<td>sending</td>
<td>SendingPayload</td>
<td>See: <a href="#messaging-sending-payload-model">SendingPayload model</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h4 id='response-json-object-1'><span id=response-json-object></span>Response (JSON object)</h4>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Key</th>
