<td>sending</td>
<td>Sending</td>
<td>See: <a href="#messaging-sending-model">Sending model</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h4 id='error-responses-1'><span id=error-responses></span>Error responses</h4>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Status</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
