<td>Unauthorized to set Sending priority</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>404</code></td>
<td>Sending not found</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>405</code></td>
<td>Sending is not editable - execution process has started or finished</td>
</tr>
